@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<style>
    :root {
        --primary-blue: #004d9e;
        --light-blue: #007ac3;
        --dark-gray: #333;
        --light-gray: #f2f2f2;
        --text-color: #555;
        --border-color: #ddd;
    }

    .privacy-container {
        padding: 2rem 0;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: auto;
    }

    .privacy-header {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--primary-blue);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .privacy-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--dark-gray);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .privacy-section {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .privacy-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--dark-gray);
        font-weight: bold;
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-blue);
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .privacy-section p,
    .privacy-section li {
        color: var(--text-color);
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .privacy-section ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .contact-info {
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--dark-gray);
    }
</style>

<div class="privacy-container">
    <h1 class="privacy-header">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p class="privacy-subtitle">VC Municipality Privacy Policy</p>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
            Welcome to the VC Municipality's official website. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and
            protect your personal information when you use our website and the Municipal Services Application. The
            application is designed to improve citizen engagement and service delivery by allowing residents to report
            issues, access local event information, and track service requests.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you use the Municipal Services Application, we may collect the following information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Service Request Details:</strong> When you report an issue, the application prompts you to
                provide details such as the location and category of the issue.</li>
            <li><strong>Media Attachments:</strong> You have the option to attach images or documents related to the
                issue you are reporting.</li>
            <li><strong>Search Queries:</strong> For the "Local Events and Announcements" feature, we may analyze user
                search patterns and preferences to provide recommendations.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>3. Use of Your Information</h2>
        <p>The information we collect is used to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Process and manage your reported issues and service requests.</li>
            <li>Provide you with updates on the status of your service requests.</li>
            <li>Improve service delivery and citizen engagement within the municipality.</li>
            <li>Suggest related or recommended events based on your search patterns and preferences.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>
            We are committed to protecting the data you provide. The application utilizes appropriate data structures to
            efficiently manage and organize reported issues. We employ various data structures, including lists, heaps,
            and trees, to ensure the efficient management and retrieval of information.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>5. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
        <p>
            VC Municipality does not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties. We
            may share your information with municipal departments or authorised service providers as necessary to
            address your reported issues and service requests.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
            You have the right to access, correct, or request the deletion of your personal information. If you have any
            questions or concerns about this privacy policy or your data, please contact us through the official
            municipal channels.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>7. Changes to this Policy</h2>
        <p>
            VC Municipality reserves the right to update this privacy policy at any time. We will notify you of any
            changes by posting the new policy on this page.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="contact-info">
            For any questions regarding this privacy policy, please contact us at [Insert Contact Information].
        </p>
    </div>
</div>